      "content": "but that \"power\" feels like such a lie. it's just a way to keep people productive while everything burns. if the ship is definitely going down, why stay on board and just endure the terror of watching it happen? wouldn't it be more peaceful to just... not be here to see it? it feels less like a choice and more like a death sentence we're all just waiting for.",
